346
00:24:01,352 --> 00:24:02,352
Quoi ?

347
00:24:04,288 --> 00:24:05,563
Tu as bien dormi ?

348
00:24:06,476 --> 00:24:07,476
Ouais.

349
00:24:12,992 --> 00:24:14,689
